query:
SELECT id, clientId, mealType, aiDescription, beverageType, beverageVolumeMl, calories, loggedAt 
FROM meals 
WHERE beverageType IS NOT NULL 
  AND beverageVolumeMl IS NOT NULL 
  AND calories = 0 
  AND protein = 0 
  AND fat = 0 
  AND carbs = 0 
  AND fibre = 0
ORDER BY loggedAt DESC;
